      "updated": 1780508576
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2067b60000000000fc3417",
      "text": "from [井戸端荘: 様々なプロット(inajob)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780508598,
      "updated": 1780508600
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2067a50000000000fc3416",
      "text": "\t>性格認識が甘いので、「誰が」をあまり書かせないほうが無難そう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780508581,
      "updated": 1780508601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a20679f0000000000fc3413",
      "text": "\t[KarpathyのLLM Wiki] + [Cosense CLI]によって井戸端民の設定データベースが作られているw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780508576,
      "updated": 1780508733
    },
    {
      "id": "6a20683d0000000000fc3418",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/dca05f28edcc044b2629048d21f9ad51]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780508733,
      "updated": 1780508775
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2068670000000000fc3419",
      "text": "\tこれは井戸端でない小説作りでも有用かもしれない？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780508775,
      "updated": 1780509016
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2095030000000000ba9c45",
      "text": "\t[KarpathyのLLM Wiki]ではないが、以前LLMに物語を作ってもらった時そういう構成にしたのを思い出した[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780520196,
      "updated": 1780520232
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2095280000000000ba9c46",
